      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "QuadTree Node Structure(Geo sharded by region data can fit the whole quad tree in a single machine upto 10M business ~5-10 GB)",
