      "fontSize": 41.299244448442074,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "text": "In memory delayed Queue: This will hold the request \nif request is currently throttled\nto retry after a second. \nHold upto 100 such requests\n\nConcern: Latency for the request increase.",
